snippet.title: Last Christmas Full Trailer
snippet.description:
Last Christmas is a classical style Point and Click Adventure Game telling a story about a young man named Frankie who is trying to prepare a perfect Christmas setting for him and his girlfriend Betty in their family cottage. But things aren't as they seem...
